The formalism developed here could however be important for\nunderstanding the porous regulation of continuum-driven, super-Eddington\noutflows from luminous blue variables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Dec 2017 00:28:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
