ects. As a related aspect of these probe\nmodifications, we also compute the Renyi-entropy $S_n$ in high energy\neigenstates on a circle. For subsystems much larger than the thermal length, we\nobtain a WKB solution to the monodromy problem, and deduce from this the\nentanglement spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Dec 2017 01:54:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 18:02:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 29 May 2018 19:22:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
