try. The model also interprets the global features of the\nobserved spectral energy distribution in radio to X-ray energy bands. We also\ndiscuss the curvature radiation and the inverse-Compton scattering process in\nthe outer gap accelerator of the WD in AR Scorpii and discuss the possibility\nof the detection by future high-energy missions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Dec 2017 08:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
